# FRONTEND ARCHITECTURE & LOGIC

## TECH STACK
- React Native with TypeScript (Expo SDK)
- NativeWind (Tailwind CSS)
- Supabase (Backend/Auth)
- Cloudinary (Media)

## PROJECT STRUCTURE (STRICT)
`src/`
 ├─ `core/`          -> config, permissions, i18n, utils, supabase client
 ├─ `design-system/` -> tokens, components, templates
 ├─ `modules/`       -> domain modules (`auth`, `dashboard`, `onboarding`)
 │   ├─ `screens/`   -> UI only
 │   ├─ `hooks.ts`   -> business logic & RHF setup
 │   ├─ `schema.ts`  -> Zod validation
 │   └─ `services/`  -> Supabase API calls
 ├─ `navigation/`    -> React Navigation setup
 └─ `store/`         -> Zustand global stores

## STATE MANAGEMENT
- Use Zustand for global state (`authStore`, `draftStore`).
- Use React Hook Form + Zod for ALL forms.
- Support "Save as Draft" logic by storing partial RHF data in Zustand before pushing to Supabase.